HR Attrition Analytics Dashboard

Objective - To help HR teams identify high-risk employee segments and improve retention strategy using data-driven insights.

This project analyzes employee attrition patterns using the IBM HR Analytics dataset.
The objective is to identify key drivers behind employee turnover and provide data-driven insights for HR decision-making.

The dashboard is divided into two pages:
 - Executive Overview
 - Root Cause Analysis (Deep Dive)

